A Form Two student has committed suicide at Kibathi village in Nyahururu after his father allegedly failed to transfer him to a school of his choice.
 The body of the student at a school in Mararal, Samburu County, was found dangling from the roof of his room by neighbours who went to visit him yesterday morning. 
